ng with a champagne bottlein the dappled swell; but presently a cloud engulfed everything, a greatwave lifted and rolled me, and soon I was too upset in all senses to tellwhether I was heading for Yalta or Tuapse. Abject fear set loose instantlythe pain I already knew, and I would have drowned there and then had not thenext billow given me a boost and deposited me near my own trousers.

